{"tid":1999743,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學英文讀音","createTime":"2020-05-03T11:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T18:10:09.000Z","uid":164985,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a277aed9eb7597bd2e9b928689d5a4a33fa187ae","tid":1999743,"uid":164985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:17:32.000Z","msg":"想幫同學仔學英文，佢地本身唔太識英文讀音，字又唔識多個，睇英文音標都係一知半解<br />\n點入手學讀音會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0509ed27b98bb8b4f31defc8a8bc52469e1eb5ae","tid":1999743,"uid":232290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"我都想學 細個個底打得唔好 大個努力緊"},{"pid":"65018b5c4bd98a7cca550db9d70544f2defc30d9","tid":1999743,"uid":190573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"咁大個人先想改發音就紮紮實實咁學IPA打好基礎，如果你有恆心，YouTube 大把免費教學"},{"pid":"c1b1e56c44ddfcac963eea9938d4e9ce8702450c","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"學phonics<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能有啲phonics學習卡咁樣，學完之後應該會見到啲regular嘅字識得讀出嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過因為英文常用字入面有85%係irregular嘅讀音，例如know同hour咁樣，所以學完phonics之後如果開始覺得唔夠用，就學IPA<br />\n<br />\nIPA嘅好處就係你可以知個字exact嘅讀音，包括好多香港人 don't give a shit嘅stress (重音)，例如Triangle 讀音應該係 ˈtraɪ.&aelig;ŋ.ɡəl/，但係好多香港會讀成 /traɪˈ&aelig;ŋ.ɡəl/，stress會擺左喺第二節<br />\n<br />\n建議用下面呢個網學：<br />\n<a href=\"http://cambridgeenglishonline.com/interactive_phonemic_chart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcambridgeenglishonline.com%2Finteractive_phonemic_chart%2F&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2f2ab572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cambridgeenglishonline.com/interactive_phonemic_chart/</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以去睇阿滴英文，佢啲片有好多都可以幫到你個friend，一下拋磚引玉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16kkr2eGSdE&amp;t=864s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D16kkr2eGSdE%26t%3D864s&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=653293b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16kkr2eGSdE&amp;t=864s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QDyyjgtDba0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQDyyjgtDba0&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=00cdedb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QDyyjgtDba0</a> (kk音標係for美國用嘅一套音標) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yyQzVesySTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyyQzVesySTc&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e45a82e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yyQzVesySTc</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上phonics可以幫你打好個底，即使有irregular嘅字其實都唔難記，不過加埋IPA你就可以知罪正確嘅讀音<br />\n<br />\n其實最重要係聽多啲，建議你個friend去睇多啲美劇，如果良心過得去嘅話睇盜版雙語字幕，或者用chrome擴充功能睇Netflix開雙語字幕 (推American Horror Story, Stranger Things, How to Get Away With Murder)，身邊冇人嘅話試下模仿住劇中人物嘅語氣講嘢 (呢招有名的，教shadowing)，揣摩一下佢地嘅語氣<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係pro，只係小弟學英文嘅過程，希望幫到你個friend，gayau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f239cd24176d04ad837c147faa2206acf7cc1d4","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:24:46.000Z","msg":"樓主如果唔介意弱智，可以試下下面呢個YouTube channel嘅片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg%2Ffeatured&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=b3832703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n幫你search phonics learning嘅時候見到的，諗起原來自己小學都係用呢個學，有啲懷念<br />\n實際佢個內容我已經唔係好記得，不過應該幾有用的，你可以試下"},{"pid":"34dfc809ce0ab986583a2fb85e225457d4d6aedc","tid":1999743,"uid":110653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f239cd24176d04ad837c147faa2206acf7cc1d4","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:24:46.000Z","msg":"樓主如果唔介意弱智，可以試下下面呢個YouTube channel嘅片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg%2Ffeatured&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=b3832703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n幫你search phonics learning嘅時候見到的，諗起原來自己小學都係用呢個學，有啲懷念<br />\n實際佢個內容我已經唔係好記得，不過應該幾有用的，你可以試下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學呢種先, 修正發音再學GB/GA其中一種"},{"pid":"74df743959cbe98f9d78a4245499d261851c2db4","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34dfc809ce0ab986583a2fb85e225457d4d6aedc","tid":1999743,"uid":110653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f239cd24176d04ad837c147faa2206acf7cc1d4","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:24:46.000Z","msg":"樓主如果唔介意弱智，可以試下下面呢個YouTube channel嘅片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg%2Ffeatured&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=b3832703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_qs3c0ehDvZkbiEbOj6Drg/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n幫你search phonics learning嘅時候見到的，諗起原來自己小學都係用呢個學，有啲懷念<br />\n實際佢個內容我已經唔係好記得，不過應該幾有用的，你可以試下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" c