1:16.000Z","msg":"聽蕭叔叔嘅舊片<br />\n英文由F字學起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新片齋chok 多過教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢嗰集教邊個音<br />\n你睇完再去BBC Learning English<br />\n睇返佢同一個音嘅教學<br />\nBBC 有多角度晒咀型好易跟<br />\n再練埋BBC 嗰堆近似音生字<br />\n要清楚分辨到佢個聲<br />\n有系統地跟住唔同種類 phonics <br />\n逐個學<br />\n<br />\n練好近音字<br />\n再練句子語氣節奏 intonation<br />\n多個字嘅連音讀法<br />\n再練日常會話<br />\n最後挑戰 tongue twister<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5387c28f70dd2d973e39be46029a64de4e3036","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c7025a792004e4c447dbec751a7fe74ab134d6","tid":1999743,"uid":110653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74df743959cbe98f9d78a4245499d261851c2db4","tid":1999743,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34dfc809ce0ab986583a2fb85e225457d4d6aedc","tid":1999743,"uid":110653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學呢種先, 修正發音再學GB/GA其中一種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"係，我自己細個原本好鐘意British Accent，不過因為聽過其他英國方言之後覺得太難同埋冇想象中咁好聽，決定想GA發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"以前無聊認真研究過一排<br />\n發覺入門GB比較有規律, 但到後尾tone果part就開始難<br />\nGA啱啱好相反, 不過整體GA易學好多學習資源都多過GB"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"真，GA資源真係多好多"},{"pid":"d34ff9d00e165d9b5acfabacae7a9eaf0b2a19fd","tid":1999743,"uid":210264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"YouTube！我係睇個YouTuber順唔順眼，把聲好唔好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCana Ko都幾好，雖然佢唔係主力教Speaking，但有D片好其實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DLmHL7-115U\